To fetch the source:
git clone https://github.com/leanagilecamp/website.git

To view the site:
1/ Go to the directory containing index.html (In october 2013: www/ or www/nouveau_site/)
2/ Lauch an http server. The simplest way is to use the python standard distribution:
python -m SimpleHTTPServer
3/ In a browser open http://localhost:8000

To push:
git remote set-url origin ssh://git@github.com/leanagilecamp/website.git

To deploy:
lftp ftp.leanagilecamp.fr

SEO:
http://webmasters.stackexchange.com/questions/47085/is-there-an-xml-sitemap-generator-with-command-line-interface-for-nginx-on-linux/47105#47105

